Time":"2019-07-02T11:53:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7230d33268102caf6b29624be309df08c3806042","tid":1278140,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:54:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1b5d5b349f774c82ab36944e42bff52b0f45af","tid":1278140,"uid":15394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:55:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請問有冇文宣/長輩圖呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n文宣組知道你地成個月都好辛苦好忙 加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a917a47ff61dc31e96540cba8567ba08fe6b3679","tid":1278140,"uid":269330,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:57:42.000Z","msg":"雖然係p牌但唔好負皮住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n面對廢中廢老經驗係：<br />\n1. 自動過濾唔啱聽既野（即係背後理念，制度暴力等等），啱聽既就無限放大（啲人好暴力）<br />\n2. 同佢地講邏輯就會話「總之咁就唔啱」<br />\n3. 同佢地講有兄弟姊妹寧死不低頭，佢地話死者俾人利用<br />\n4. 覺得而家生活好好，一切美好既野都俾電視見到既破壞哂<br />\n<br />\n所以由2014諗到而家都唔知可以用咩方法溝通，但似乎個問題在於佢地唔覺得政府做左衰野，亦唔認為送中23條國教等等會關自己事，諗到既係要解決點樣令佢地知道生活上所有野都關政府同政治事，同埋大家唔係搗亂，係為成個社會爭取應得既權益<br />\n<br />\n雖然有人話我地長命過佢地，唔好忘記而家日日都放緊150個落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以輿論唔想打都要打，巴絲有計仔請接力"},{"pid":"9d360cd87708cc53db15af72e32545002da52c39","tid":1278140,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:02:07.000Z","msg":"咩宣言？"},{"pid":"d549f78d783f929af09de2a0542beee155ea3767","tid":1278140,"uid":