s=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:34:59.000Z","msg":"找數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:38:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d9af9648a22ea0056bd221179ded0f6b1ece9a","tid":1278140,"uid":34742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:38:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"07eb618db2483d40791fe505df03837a045afb59","tid":1278140,"uid":90601,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:39:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vQBm0CD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvQBm0CD.png&h=8bb1297c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位親愛的香港市民，<br />\n<br />\n我們是一群來自民間的示威者。今天，我們捨身成仁，決定進佔香港特區政府立法會。<br />\n<br />\n市民於6月起進行多次示威活動，當中更包括二百萬遊行，懇求希望政府撤回修例，而政府置若岡聞，不諳民情，竟置香港大眾、民意於不顧，甚至以民為敵。<br />\n<br />\n現任特區政府已非港人所願，所承認，立法會選舉制度更無法表達民意，尤以功能組別為甚，純淪為政治工具，所以我們不得不進行各種佔領，不合作、乃至今日進佔立法會行動。<br />\n<br />\n我們佔領者，現在政府立法會，正式宣讀五大訴求：<br />\n<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今後及之前為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況，設立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n最後我們覺得問題的根源，是香港人仍然沒有立法會及行政長官的全面普選，所以我們要求<br />\n<br />\n五、2020年立法會全面普選<br />\n<br />\n「反送中運動」發展至今，有三位年輕市民殉道。我們心繫家園，付出身軀只是想守護我家。我等未忘憂憤，然心存善念，不願香港再有為民主、為自由、為公義再添亡魂。希望社會大眾團結一致，對抗惡法，對抗暴政，共同守護香港。<br />\n<br />\n香港人宣言<br />\n<br />\nDeclaration of Hong Kong Protesters (English Ver. Draft)<br />\n<br />\nDear HongKongers,<br />\n<br />\nWe are the protesters. We have no choice but to do what we did today. The Special Administrative Region of Hong Kong of Communist China has been running the reign for twenty two years, with HongKongers' lives rotting in hell everyday. Yet the government, instead of improving HongKongers' lives as their top priority, use every means to send HongKongers and world citizens to the Chinese prisons, incl. pushing the China Extradiction Bill with lies and violence. Under such tyranny, we must bring together our conscience and loving hearts, to do all forms of civil disobedience, including occupying the Legislative Council. Fellow HongKongers may criticize our actions, but if you get to the bottom of it: Why did the community tear apart? Why did the people rage? Why do HongKongers need to be sent to Chinese prisons? Therefore we wish the government can come back, and answer our five humble requests:<br />\n<br />\n1. Withdraw the Extradition Bill, and never propose it again;<br />\n2. Withdraw the statement on &quot;Riot&quot;;<br />\n3. Withdraw the prosecution against all protestors;<br />\n4. Investigate the abuse of power of Police;<br />\n5. Use an Executive Order to disband the Legislative Council, and proceed with Dual True Elections immediately.<br />\n<br />\nThe Anti-China Extradition Movement has already taken three heroic lives. We never forget, we always remember, but we no longer want any more deaths to be added. We unite, we reject unjust laws, we fight against tyranny, and we are HongKongers.<br />\n<br />\nYours Faithfully,<br />\nThe Protestors."},{"pid":"6bf8e4caef0b0f4d83b434da0e680f50f622b328","tid":1278140,"uid":147792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b788876c4f0c60f9f532e1c6302af7c8c38b6a0","tid":1278140,"uid":137808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66f4ae20deb244081b119db8313812d0f6424f39","tid":1278140,"uid":147792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41f15e2b0e3a7823808209b098f2ac88bb7e9252","tid":1278140,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},