2fd6c9a15640b8a9f6c00b5707c8fc","tid":1278140,"uid":34742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:53:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd6a1182148df32578f640072ffc175f07549a93","tid":1278140,"uid":34742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:56:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fcbfed74bad869bba1ec09c020c87eac4c06a96f","tid":1278140,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7da3779e4f6a82145e83724e65f519791c32c48","tid":1278140,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a6b5320bbb8096cdad64eb8e5f579a9716b01b3","tid":1278140,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:40:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1276561/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1276561/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GtAGjsT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGtAGjsT.png&h=fc289683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k9b6vzG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk9b6vzG.png&h=d21eeb6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n己亥宣言"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:51:40.000Z","msg":"香港人宣言係個draft?<br />\n<br />\n金鐘宣言嘅進化版係己亥宣言？除咗頭尾之外都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:56:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位香港市民，<br />\n<br />\n我們是一群來自民間的示威者。萬不得已，我們並不想走上以身對抗暴政的路，以佔領香港特區政府立法會作為我們談判的籌碼；但滿口謊言、滿口歪理的政府卻無意回應香港人不斷走上街的訴求。我們只好以公義、良知、以及對香港、對香港人無窮無盡的愛，去抗衡橫蠻的政府。<br />\n<br />\n香港特區政府成立至今22年，政經民生每況愈下。現任特首林鄭月娥上台後，情況變本加厲，更漠視民間逾百萬民意，推出「送中惡法」。市民於6月起前仆後繼，各盡其力，或和平、或理性、或奮勇、或受傷流血，以一顆熱愛香港之心，懇求政府撤回修例，而政府置若罔聞，不諳民情，竟置香港大眾於不顧，甚至以民為敵。<br />\n<br />\n現任特區政府已非以港人行先，為使政府聆聽港人聲音，我等市民不得不進行各種佔領，不合作運動、乃至今日佔領立法會行動。社會或對我等佔領者有所批評，但追本溯源，社會撕裂之誘因為何？民怨每日俱增之本源為何？香港何辜？香港人何以被追逼至此？我等港人沒有武裝，沒有暴力，只能以秉持正義於心，無畏無懼，奮勇向前。希望能香港政府能及時回首，重回正軌：<br />\n<br />\n我們佔領者，要求政府完成五大訴求：<br />\n<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n「反送中運動」發展至今，在三位年輕市民殉道。我等未忘憂憤，然心存善念，不願香港再有為民主、為自由、為公義再添亡魂。希望社會大眾團結一致，對抗惡法，對抗暴政，共同守護香港。<br />\n<br />\nDear Hong Kong citizens<br />\n<br />\nWe are a group of protesters. Today, we have decided to occupy the Hong Kong Legislative Council.<br />\n<br />\nSince early June, the people of Hong Kong have been expressing their demands through various demonstrations. Not only did two million of us take to the street, three youngsters even sacrificed their lives for this anti-extradition-law movement, in hopes of demanding the full withdrawal of the bill. Yet the government continues to shamelessly ignore the will of the people, and remains indifferent to our demands. The government has even set us up as its enemy.<br />\n<br />\nThe current SAR administration no longer represents the will of the people of Hong Kong. The electoral system for the Legislative Council is incapable of reflecting public opinion, and functional constituencies, in particular, have become mere political tools. As such, we as citizens have no choice but to carry out a series of occupying and non-cooperative campaigns, leading to the occupation of the Legislative Council today.<br />\n<br />\nWe, the occupiers of the Legislative Council, officially make the following five demands:<br />\n<br />\n1) Fully withdraw the Proposed Amendments<br />\n2) Rescind the characterization of the movement as a &ldquo;Riot&rdquo;<br />\n3) Drop all charges against anti-extradition protestors<br />\n4) Set up an independent investigation committee, fully investigate and hold accountable abuses of power and violence in the Hong Kong Police Force<br />\n<br />\nLastly, we believe that the root cause of the political crisis is the lack of universal suffrage in electing members of the Legislative Council and the Chief Executive, therefore, we demand that the authorities:<br />\n<br />\n5) Implement Universal Suffrage of the Executive and Legislature by 2020<br />\n<br />\nSince the beginning of the anti-extradition movement, three young citizens have already died. Our hearts are with our homeland, and we put our lives on the line to defend it. We do not want to see more martyrs in Hong Kong&rsquo;s long struggle for democracy and freedom. We hope that society remains united, and join us in resisting the unjust bill, the oppressive government, and together, protect Hong Kong."},{"pid":"b2b605d628c788315f17586c46bef5e3672f8872","tid":1278140,"uid":150742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:57:59.000Z","msg":"啱呀屌"},{"pid":"4d3153afa8f8c9d49abeb0ae3db30aee3faf5990","tid":1278140,"uid":34742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:07:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd7b8dafcdc8e974f2fc7216581de398962aa1e4","tid":1278140,"uid":267172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:07:14.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a89f61d35911411dfa35939eef7c201be8a76e42","tid":1278140,"uid":219244,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd6a1182148df32578f640072ffc175f07549a93","tid":1278140,"uid":34742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:56:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:09:59.000Z","msg":"真係<br />\n今次俾政府成功引導去暴力衝擊同大肆破壞<br />\n好多人都以為示威者就咁衝入去洩憤就出返嚟<br />\n<br />\n但其實衝入立法會宣讀宣言真係好有象徵意義囉<br />\n可惜全每個焦點都去晒另一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a2607b9948d0e127b637ab57c25241ef7d9596","tid":1278140,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:11:54.000Z","msg":"推上水先，最重點既野，要宣傳出去，呢個係大家辛苦咁耐既終極目標 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a86763866d9ce7f69cb0c934556a12ea31caeeb","tid":1278140,"uid":3